  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x2D2A0", "zh": "近身战我更胜一筹！"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x2D2BC", "zh": "好了……看我把你切碎！"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x2D2DC", "zh": "可、可恶！到头了……！"},
